{"tid":316673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉…今日派位點知俾人串到喊-.-","createTime":"2017-07-11T01:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T14:45:51.000Z","uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b551f12f6ee4d7aec75cdbfcdabbf05167a2d3","tid":316673,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:53:20.000Z","msg":"今日見啲同學成班圍埋一齊講派位嘢<br />\n我想搭下嗲 點知佢地話我講野1999派唔到第一志願=.= <br />\n我話：你班傻的嗎仔緊係聽唔明我講乜啦，我智商300，所以你哋同我溝通唔到姐 <br />\n然後其中一個同學聽到之後話：哦&hellip; 原來我哋智商差成200咁多，唔怪之得啦&hellip;<br />\n咁我又接住講：算啦我都唔介意嘅<br />\n點知佢哋竟然話我弱智仔 <br />\n仲同我講：我哋呢度每個人嘅智商都係500以上<br />\n又叫我死開啦白痴仔&hellip; 咁＝︿＝ <br />\n聽到佢地咁講我忍唔住流咗少少眼淚然後跑走咗<br />\n不過當時我仲係好型棍&gt;3&lt;<br />\n我決定唔讀中一啦，以後日日上連登hi你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3a876cbe62e7f2eb28452e44057928b9bbeed","tid":316673,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T01:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc918724866cb1d7a8bc212a793fab2fb478043","tid":316673,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a8ca782619b72695a641813cdbaaf428e1d742d","tid":316673,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:04:59.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"4823ee027128646a21568269221bbe7c2801e928","tid":316673,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"On9!"},{"pid":"e4c6205da7c250f88b1856de4b112a7e3d9285c9","tid":316673,"uid":15473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:05:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Show Blocked User - 聖誕快樂</blockquote><br />\n我唔信"},{"pid":"daf461ce039a4f90a52b2206e555132fbe0b1c8d","tid":316673,"uid":115323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T02:07:24.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"ecfe4ad1f74cbdce2d940eb866d947a98a